      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOLD STRIPES (1) turned in a plain performance last time when sixth at this track over 390m behind Molly Mckayla (22.87) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Key runner on his best form. MOONLIGHT JAZZ (2) hit the ground running from the squeeze draw with a slick early split, holding on for a minor placing when third and beaten 4 lengths at this track over 390m in 22.37. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from four starts. Expected to be in this for a long way. ASTON GIRL (6) recorded her best time this course and distance latest, finishing a half a length second behind Aston Cleese in 22.27. Has the ability and can measure up. PATRIOT NIAMH (5) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at her latest outing at this circuit.",
